data.text:
Those who have given their lives for our country during this stupid war!!

You do not have to be for the war in Iraq to know that these young men and women fought with all their heart for our country. I write this list on my blog to honor those who have given the most final and precious gift of all, their lives.

The War Dead -- Long May We Remember Them
